{"id":767744,"url":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Louis_Lombardi","text":"Louis Lombardi Jr. (born January 17, 1968) is an American actor. He is known for his roles as Edgar Stiles in the Fox series \"24\" and Skip Lipari in the HBO series \"The Sopranos\". His other television work includes \"Fantasy Island\", \"Mob City\", \"Entourage\", \"Heroes\" and \"CSI\".\nLombardi's movie credits include \"Beer League\", \"The Usual Suspects\", \"Natural Born Killers\", \"Suicide Kings\", \"Beverly Hills Cop III\", \"The Animal\", \"Spider-Man 2\", \"3000 Miles to Graceland\", \"The Crew\", \"The Hot Chick\", \"The Spirit\", \"Battleship\" and \"Jersey Boys\". He also wrote, directed and starred in the movie \"Dough Boys\" (2008).\nLombardi was born in The Bronx, New York City.","categories":[],"infobox_types":[],"annotations":[{"uri":"Americans","surface_form":"American","offset":49},{"uri":"FOX","surface_form":"Fox","offset":114},{"uri":"24_(TV_series)","surface_form":"24","offset":126},{"uri":"HBO","surface_form":"HBO","offset":153},{"uri":"The_Sopranos","surface_form":"The Sopranos","offset":165},{"uri":"Fantasy_Island_(1998_TV_series)","surface_form":"Fantasy Island","offset":216},{"uri":"Mob_City","surface_form":"Mob City","offset":234},{"uri":"Entourage_(TV_series)","surface_form":"Entourage","offset":246},{"uri":"Heroes_(U.S._TV_series)","surface_form":"Heroes","offset":259},{"uri":"Crime_Scene_Investigation","surface_form":"CSI","offset":272},{"uri":"Beer_League","surface_form":"Beer League","offset":312},{"uri":"The_Usual_Suspects","surface_form":"The Usual Suspects","offset":327},{"uri":"Natural_Born_Killers","surface_form":"Natural Born Killers","offset":349},{"uri":"Suicide_Kings","surface_form":"Suicide Kings","offset":373},{"uri":"Beverly_Hills_Cop_III","surface_form":"Beverly Hills Cop III","offset":390},{"uri":"The_Animal","surface_form":"The Animal","offset":415},{"uri":"Spider-Man_2","surface_form":"Spider-Man 2","offset":429},{"uri":"3000_Miles_to_Gracela